name: LE-BO2D9 (Leebo) (V)
Lore: 'Smuggler. Heavily modified Cybot Galactica LE-series repair droid. Information broker. Provides information gained through underworld channels to the Alliance.',
Text: 'May be battled. If with Dash Rendar, adds one destiny to attrition only. Once per turn, if at a battleground, you may peek at the top card of opponent''s Reserve Deck; may place that card on top of opponent''s Used Pile.',
